OL,3,CFootball fan 'ashamed' and hopes
OL,4,Cothers 'think twice' about tragedy
OL,5,Cchanting
OL,7,FHe told Manchester Magistrates' Court:
OL,8,F"I just want to reiterate that I'm
OL,9,Fjust deeply sorry and I really regret
OL,10,Fwhat I did. I'm ashamed and
OL,11,Fembarrassed.
OL,13,F"Everyone that knows me has obviously
OL,14,Ffelt this as well. It's just a
OL,15,Fdifficult situation. I wish it never
OL,16,Fwould have happened. I regret it
OL,17,Fterribly.
OL,19,F"I hope other people look on what's
OL,20,Fhappened to me and think twice before
OL,21,Fthey do anything at football games."
