OL,7,FTess Kenyon, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fcourt the case involved "tragedy
OL,9,Fchanting" at the Old Trafford game on
OL,10,F17 March, which was won 4-3 by
OL,11,FManchester United.
OL,13,FA video from an account on X was
OL,14,Fplayed in which Avery could be seen
OL,15,Fputting his hand over his face with
OL,16,Fhis fingers splayed.
OL,18,FThe court heard the gesture was a
OL,19,Freference to the , in which 97
OL,20,FLiverpool fans died following a crush
OL,21,Fat the 1989 FA Cup semi-final.
