OL,7,FAvery was also seen pushing with two
OL,8,Fhands, which the court was told was a
OL,9,Freference to the Heysel stadium
OL,10,Fdisaster, where 39 people died at a
OL,11,Fmatch between Juventus and Liverpool.
OL,13,FThe defendant, wearing a black long-
OL,14,Fsleeved polo-shirt, sat with his head
OL,15,Fdown as the short video was played
OL,16,Ftwice.
