OL,7,FMs Kenyon said: "The defendant's
OL,8,Fgestures are abusive in the context of
OL,9,Fwhat they denote and they were
OL,10,Fdirected towards Liverpool fans at
OL,11,Fthis football match."
OL,13,FShe told the court the video went
OL,14,Fviral online and the following day the
OL,15,Fdefendant presented himself at a
OL,16,Fpolice station where he told officers
OL,17,Fpeople were "getting the wrong end of
OL,18,Fthe stick".
