OL,7,FIan Huggan, defending, said Avery was
OL,8,Fa "family man" with a job in the
OL,9,Fconstruction industry.
OL,11,FHe said: "He feels that he has not
OL,12,Fonly let himself down but his family
OL,13,Fand close friends."
OL,15,FMagistrates told Avery, of Cranham
OL,16,FRoad, Manchester, he was banned from
OL,17,Ffrom attending football matches in the
OL,18,FUK for three years and would have to
OL,19,Fsurrender his passport when certain
OL,20,Fgames were played outside the UK.
